title: Hentai / Hot Juicy Teacher 1-2-3 avi
description:
Japenese with English subs 

Hot Juicy Teacher - Vol 1

The story takes place at a top ranking prestegious school where two students attend. Yuichiro 
Date, a student who was framed as a rapist at his old school and have been causing trouble ever 
since. Hiromi Mizuki, a student who can not stand up for himself and is always being bullied on. 
Yuichiro is here to revenge on all female teachers. Thus Hiromi, is here to protect the one that 
he loves... 


Hot Juicy Teacher - Vol 2


Yuichiro continues to plot his revenge against the Hot Juicy Teachers while Hiromi continues to 
bare the punishment to protect the one he loves. Same place, same time, two different stories. 
How will the two different sides connect with each other? There's only one way to find out... Hot 
Juicy Teacher is back with even more heat packed in, enjoy! 


Hot Juicy Teacher - Vol 3

Hiromi meets Mikoto Todo, sister of Honoka Todo. He becomes close with her and she offers Hiromi to 
have her sister protect him. Yuichiro now has two teachers as his personal slave, but his conquest 
does not end there. He now has his eyes on Honoka Todo! You'll be shocked with the outcome of this 
final installment of Hot Juicy Teacher!
